{"type": "article", "id": 22680, "title": "想要经典购物清单，请看电商Mr Porter周年特别款", "description": "这应该是男士们“最不容易出错的购物清单之一”", "date": "2016-02-23T08:30:09Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1241, "name": "男装"}, {"id": 319, "name": "电商"}, {"id": 23789, "name": "精选"}, {"id": 19410, "name": "购物清单"}, {"id": 3677, "name": "衬衫"}, {"id": 23790, "name": "礼帽"}, {"id": 9350, "name": "风衣"}, {"id": 8914, "name": "Mr Porter"}, {"id": 12763, "name": "Maison Margiela"}, {"id": 9352, "name": "MACKINTOSH"}], "category": 19, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 206, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071247034BrVEGdp5ehw8cto.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>要是提及全球范围内最受欢迎的男装电商，当属<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com\"> MR PORTER</a>，这个售卖高端及奢侈男装品牌的平台，从页面、精选的商品到网站上的<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/journal/\">博客 The Journal</a> 都以好品味而著称。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124655bj01girH4Jw6oP2E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69848485\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>最近，他们迎来了五周年生日，庆贺方式则是找来了一些他们团队钟爱且一直合作的品牌，从它们最受欢迎的基本款单品中选择，重新推出以 MR PORTER 最常见的黑、白、灰为主的款式，作为 MR PORTER 五周年特别款。</p>\n<p class=\"\">如果是想穿着更有品味、更成熟简约的男士，就不要错过这份包含 20 件精选单品的清单，换言之，这应该是“最不容易出错的购物清单之一”。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071246564EL6R3AIxbV2YTuQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">MR PORTER 表示五周年的合作，对于经典款来说必须是一些“历史悠久”的权威品牌。从这方面考虑，眼镜框架找来了具有 40 多年历史的英国手工眼镜品牌 <a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-cutler-and-gross-d-frame-tortoiseshell-acetate-sunglasses/696450?ppv=2\">Cutler And Gross</a> 的 <a href=\"https://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-cutler-and-gross-d-frame-tortoiseshell-acetate-sunglasses/696450?ppv=2\">D-Frame Tortoiseshell Acetate 太阳镜</a>，电影《王牌特工》当中科林叔戴的就是这个牌子。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071246562aGIw1Siypb0RnjV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52844639\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">还有 Maison Margiela 的<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-maison-margiela-suede-trimmed-cashmere-sweater/700297?ppv=2\">黑色肘部补丁山羊绒毛衣（Suede-Trimmed Cashmere Sweater）</a>。下图中小小的黑色礼帽 pin，便是此次 Mr Porter 五周年的 logo。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071246568RJOsHUDP2054Njq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.59336609\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></figure><div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"></figure><p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124657ENF54ZzPATwh1Gi0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">上图这几件上衣也值得一试，模特上身的灰色卫衣来自美国设计师品牌 <a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-todd-snyder-x-champion-stretch-cotton-sweatshirt/709763?ppv=2\">Todd Snyder 和运动休闲品牌 Champion 的联名款</a>。</figure><div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"></figure><p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124657xK7Y1grZlFJktWIc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52844639\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">而法国鳄鱼<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-lacoste-slim-fit-cotton-pique-polo-shirt/697981?ppv=2\">（Lacoste）的 Polo 衫</a>，简约到只剩下胸前标志性小鳄鱼 logo。</figure><div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"></figure><p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124658Tv9xXMoYIwrVEpAt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52844639\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">最经典的条纹衫也要有一件，试试<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-a-p-c-breton-striped-cotton-t-shirt/704635?ppv=2\">来自法国极简品牌 A.P.C 的</a>，从面料到 logo 细小的刺绣都是彰显品质的细节。</figure><div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"></figure><p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124658uxlUyk7mNTeqoJIt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52844639\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124659LMK3ilZadrYzE2Cx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></figure><p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p>而说到这些单品拥有的一些小精致细节，这个系列里就有很多了，比如这件 <a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-gitman-vintage-slim-fit-button-down-collar-cotton-oxford-shirt/690829?ppv=2\">Gitman Vintage 扣角领修身牛津衬衫</a>，门襟处的一块黑色绸缎，这是为 MR PORTER 制作的特别款。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124659rzHdU4Y8OGuDmbfP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56294537\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p>而英国老牌风衣品牌<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-mackintosh-cotton-raincoat/693071?ppv=2\"> Mackintosh 的黑色防水风衣</a>也在其中，全黑的设计，只有领子翻过来的内衬使用了黑白圆点花纹布料。（<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/17256.html\">想了解更多关于这个牌子的故事，可以点击这篇</a>。）</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060712470064kY18MChN2psqAI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52844639\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></figure><p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124700brG5YjWe8FcBDiTs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">配饰部分的<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-lock-co-hatters-felt-bowler-hat/705344?ppv=2\">圆顶礼帽</a>，选择了成立于 1676 年的伦敦制帽企业 Lock &amp; Co，此前深受英国皇家贵族的喜爱。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124700IxAY13qJPW8Oymrn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60427136\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">而这份清单中出现的两双鞋，则分别来自爱马仕旗下高端定制<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-john-lobb-lopez-grained-leather-penny-loafers/695255?ppv=2\">男鞋品牌  John Lobb</a>的乐福鞋以及新锐的<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-common-projects-original-achilles-leather-sneakers/692454?ppv=2\">高端球鞋代表 Common Projects</a> 最经典的“小白鞋”，正式场合和休闲场合这两双鞋足以应对一切。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124701pZzcyOXvA7mECjso.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52844639\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124701woaSc9n3Qj6l80Ob.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607124702a50ormIJZnF6zTOG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52844639\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\">最后，是一款<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/mens/mr_porter/-berluti-time-off-grained-leather-backpack/709090?ppv=2\">皮质双肩包</a>，来自成立于 1895 年的经典鞋履及皮具品牌 Berluti，不论是包袋的轮廓、正面侧面拼接的颜色，或者触感极佳的皮质面料及山羊皮衬里，都代表可以背上多年。</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071247026Adlvi7soEDckJQw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071247033DpmcBSjWtIY7E0X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52844639\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">（<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/journal/the-edit/the-5th-anniversary-collection/672\">完整列表请点击 MR PORTER 官网网址</a>）</p>\n\n\n"}